rtners. They exist solely to get the whole world grinding, vibing, jiving and forgetting each others differences which leads to great by-products namely HAPPINESS and PEACE. Their music testifies to their aims which is unusual and big. Cos they know that to have aim small is a crime in todays world.\r\n\r\nInitially, it was hard work for them to get people listen to their music. They were an unknown band making unfamiliar music in the sub continent. But over time, converting the first time hesitant listener into an instant fan became cake-walk. Band LOW RHYDERZ is the driving force of Brand LOW RHYDEZ. Versatility and style is the key to all the music they make and the business they do. However, Urban (Hip hop , Rap and Reggae) music will always be their basic thing and they say,  Our lives relate to it automatically, naturally, lyrically, metaphorically and emotionally .\r\n\r\nThough they started over three years ago, they are still on a journey with notable performances including The National Equestrian and Horse Ridding Championship ( Pondicherry ), India Mens Fashion Fair ( Bangalore ), Tata Teas Jago Re campaign at Wipro Campus ( Bangalore ), Colour nites by Bangalore Times ( Bangalore ) and other performances in prominent night clubs across South Indian States. RAVE magazine wrote about LOW RHYDERZ after witnessing them live in 2007. Their work was also acknowledged by a leading daily tabloid called the Deccan Chronicle. \r\n\r\nTwo of their music videos drew attention when they were aired by Indias leading English news channel CNN IBN in 2007 and 2009 respectively. The first video and soundtrack depicted the evolution of 60 years of Indian independence. The second one was a politically aggressive message to the youth specially, which was part of the CNN IBNs ROCK THE VOTE campaign during the Great Indian General Elections. Theyve recorded and performed with countrys leading Djs, Musicians & artists from France, Cameroon, Tanzania, Iran and Oman . \r\n\r\nRight now, be the first to know that the much anticipated debut album OUTTA NOWHERE is dropping this year. Bookings are open for live performances.One can also get them to rock events as a DJ-MC combo for dance parties ! Life is Beautiful !.. SHANTI--V-- !\r\n\r\n\r\nLOW RHYDERZ Unit Members\r\n\r\nEmCEEs :\r\n\r\nCHARLES DICKENSON\r\nmAIn-E-yAk\r\nXSTACY SASH\r\nKING JASSIM\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\nSAMUAL RAJ - PHOTOGRAPHER\r\n\r\n','lowrhyderz@gmail.com','http://www.facebook.com/pages/LOW-RHYDERZ/338472350215','http://www.lowrhyderzallday.com','','','338472350215','2305',0,NULL,NULL,'2012-09-06 07:27:31','2012-09-06 07:27:31',0,'','','low-rhyderz'),(379,0,2,2,'Last Ride Home','They Started off by releasing their first single, \'Best you\'d see\' in August \'10 and since then they have been getting a lot of invitations for fests and gigs\r\nAnd they released their second single, \'Scream Your Name\' in September \'11\r\nThey have performed and won in many fests:\r\n\r\nThe Big Band Theory (Grand Exito) 10\'\r\nUmang 10\'\r\nViva 10\'\r\nColosseum 10\'\r\nYuvana 11\'\r\nThe Uprising 10\'\r\nVividh 10\'\r\nKshitij 12\'\r\nKa-Ching 12\'\r\n\r\nThey were also The Finalists of Channel [v] Launch Pad (Mumbai Round)\r\nand have done a few gigs at Not Just Jazz By the Bay, and at Irish pub.','Dev +919920522281(PIN 28B1CFDB)','http://www.facebook.com/lastridehome','http://www.reverbnation.com/lastridehome4','','http://www.reverbnation.com/lastridehome4','240390139285','2297',0,NULL,NULL,'2012-09-06 07:27:31','2012-09-06 07:27:31',0,'','','last-ride-home'),(380,2,1,1,'Acrid Semblance','Formed in the year 2002 by Anubhav and Kshitish and subsequently joined by Vikas, Cj and Ashim, the band is hailed as the pioneer melodic death metal act in India. \r\n\r\nIn a scene predominated by cover ridden acts, the band burst onto the scene with original material demonstrating virtuoso like skills and yet stay rooted in the classic bang your head metal.\r\n\r\nThe well received demo Soul Corrosion paved the way for band going on a two city tour in 2003 which was not a widespread thing to do for brand new bands back then.\r\nFollowing it up with the widely anticipated and eventually thoroughly appreciated by critics and fans alike, the debut full length From the oblivion cemented the position of the band as a premier melodic act from the country. \r\n\r\nIn 2008, the Mindgames EP made way for even larger fan bases with the song clocking over 10,000 plays in the first 3 months on the guitar hero like game portal Jamlegend.\r\n\r\nThe band is currently working on putting finishing touches to From the oblivion\'s follow up.','anubhav@acridsemblance.com','http://www.facebook.com/acridsemblance','http://www.acridsemblance.com','http://soundcloud.com/acridsemblance','','200708812755','2293',0,NULL,1,'2012-09-06 07:27:31','2012-10-09 11:52:51',185,'[\"anubhav@acridsemblance.com\\r\",\"\\r\",\"\"]','[\"\"]','acrid-semblance'),(381,0,29,29,'Cassini\'s Division','Cassinis Division, the premier Indian rock band that has been steadily gaining in popularity since its inception in 2001.\r\n\r\nThe band was formed with a view of promoting original contemporary rock music that has a cutting edge and universal appeal while being rooted in the Indian ethos. Much of the bands music can be described as song-centric alternative rock with hybrid sonic influences ranging from pop to hard rock.\r\n\r\nAs the Indian rock music movement continues to grow steadily the band has come to be seen as one of the pioneering original bands who first took the step of moving away from the cover band scene that existed till the end of the nineties.','','http://www.facebook.com/cassinisdivision','http://www.cassinisdivision.com','http://soundcloud.com/cassini-division','http://www.reverbnation.com/cassinisdivision','16400510039','2290',0,NULL,NULL,'2012-09-06 07:27:31','2012-09-06 07:27:31',0,'','','cassinis-division'),(382,0,1,1,'Dj Rahul Vaidya','In the field of Dj\'ing/Remixing the hottest talent