\nPink Floyd, The Verve) at Yash Raj Studios in Mumbai.\r\n\r\nIn 2009 Medusa performed at the Great Escape Festival in Brighton and\r\ncontinued their UK tour to Cardiff, Oxford, Liverpool and London','098218-83037 / email: vidhi.jhaveri@gmail.com','http://www.facebook.com/hellomedusa','','','','34740778780','2197',0,NULL,NULL,'2012-09-06 07:27:31','2012-09-06 07:27:31',0,'','','medusa'),(397,0,64,64,'Fallen Grace','Fallen Grace is a melodic death metal band based in Colombo, Sri Lanka.\r\n\r\nFallen Grace was instigated in Colombo, Sri Lanka by five budding musicians from D.S.Senanayake College, who shared the same passion for adrenaline, aggression and intoxication in late 2003 at a time when Hard Rock & Metal music in the country was severely occult and even unheard of. The music industry was awash gangster-rappers, disgusting pop singers and mundane club bands that played the same set of covers every night! A change was in dire need! It was this drive to be different, to be original and to create music which was raw and above all with substance, that created the nucleus of Fallen Grace and which still drives the band to this day!\r\n\r\nOur common belief is that were put on this planet to create and play music and nothing else! Our devotion to our art is ardent. Managing day jobs and college while carrying the band forward is not an easy task, especially in a country with very little or no backers for this particular genre of music. But as a band it is our central belief that if there is a will, there is a way. Due to five years of sheer live insanity and the good word of mouth, Fallen Grace have risen from the occult and have become a much sort after band not only in the Heavy Metal scene but also in the larger English Music Industry in Sri Lanka.\r\n\r\nFallen Grace have now laid the ground work for their debut studio release titled Heresy Unveiled (Do we believe?). The album is currently being recorded by the Expounder at Empyre Studios, Colombo. The album deals with the corruption of leaders, apathy, damaged caused by organized religion and blood-shed Sri Lankans deal with at present!\r\n','artstudio666@gmail.com/fallengracesl@gmail.com','http://www.facebook.com/fallengracesl','http://www.myspace.com/fallengracesl','','','242657572318','2193',0,NULL,NULL,'2012-09-06 07:27:31','2012-09-06 07:27:31',0,'','','fallen-grace'),(398,0,3,3,'Divine Raaga','Divine Raaga is an Indian Rock band formed in the city of Bangalore. Their style of playing ranges from Sufiyana and Indian-light to semi-classical and rock. But the one thing that is common among most of their songs is the sense of connection with the heavens; hence the name, Divine Raaga.','admin@divineraaga.com','http://www.facebook.com/divineraaga','http://www.divineraaga.in','','','153325751507','2188',0,NULL,NULL,'2012-09-06 07:27:31','2012-09-06 07:27:31',0,'','','divine-raaga'),(399,0,104,104,'DeathRap ( Rappers From Hyderabad City )','\'DeathRap\' is the style of rap which revolves around violent, gore, brutal and explicit lyrics of Gangster rap.  But, the \r\nlyrics of this genre are more violent than that of Gangster Rap.\r\nBut, hence people of our region are much addicted to romantic and emotional types of raps, so we also work on this genre\'s of rap.\r\n\r\n\'DeathRap\' - a hip-hop crew of young rappers from Hyderabad, started in late 2010, when we members\r\ncame together and shake our hands.\r\nThe members of our crew were sole rappers before we formed this, but our aim got strong\r\nwhen we all came together.\r\nWe make our own compositons and lyrics, and record those on different genres such as :\r\nromantic, emotional, hip-hop, thug life etc., and love to work on a variety of attractive beats, and display the tracks to you in various styles.\r\nWe also do live performances on various venues.\r\nWe believe in faith and unity. \r\n\r\nOur first Mixtape is out, which includes 9 tracks.\r\n\r\nWe hope for a best career. And with your love, respect and support, we are now all set to reach heights.','9966981212-9966081212','http://www.facebook.com/DeathRapHyderabadCity','www.youtube.com/deathraphyd','',' www.reverbnation.com/deathrap','114687358602562','2187',0,NULL,NULL,'2012-09-06 07:27:31','2012-09-06 07:27:31',0,'','','deathrap-rappers-from-hyderabad-city'),(400,0,92,92,'DEATHKNELL','DEATHKNELL is a heavy metal / classic rock band originated from the streets of shimla....Inspired by various different metal,rock iconic figures makes their music much more versatile n gives them a wide range of thoughts processed down in their compositions...The band mainly consists of three members who have a very definite role in the band...most of the gigs are done by the three of them but in some cases,according to the requirement of the gig they add a touring member to the band.....If you are looking for some cool guitar riffs, long extended soulful solos here\'s the guitarist for you who loves to show off his playing giving all that the song demands for... Backed by the drummer whose not only limited to the beats but also does the composing n gets his hand down writing some very meaningful lyrics for the band gives the band a great strength...The bassist of the band has a very likeable n crazy stage presence making a wild connection n relation with the audience...So far the band has come out with some great interesting compositions which have been liked n appreciated by the people..Some of the songs composed are on the thoughts which are generally ignored by the society n some have a very deep personal feelings attached to it....The band has a good number of some major gigs and originals under their belt and are looking forward to release their debut album...\r\n','','http://www.facebook.com/deathknelld2','http://www.deathknell.in','','http://www.reverbnation.com/deathknell','164799014126','2183',0,NULL,NULL,'2012-09-06 07:27:31','2012-09-06 07:27:31',0,'','','deathknell'),(401,0,15,15,'Area 231','After a year, of replacing missing