lented and innovative. He adds the extra excitement to the show and is very enthusiastic.\r\n\r\nAshish Shyam_ is the bass guitarist and loves his guitar as if its his girlfriend. He is the heartbeat of the band and steals all hearts away. He is the most experienced and extremely talented.\r\n\r\n\r\nRajesh Rana _He is the drummer cum percussionist and terms of the speed of is hands and feet and the wonderful, percussive \"ideas\" he is convevys of drums. He is extremely energetic,experienced and talented.He is an indispensible member of the band and gets the rocking feeling to the music .\r\n\r\nHayat Ahmad_ is the rythm guitarist and backup vocals . He is extremely talented and innovative and the backbone of the band as everything depends on his rythm.he is extremely talented and experienced.\r\n\r\n*-TERMS & CONDITIONS FOR ANY PERFORMANCE OFFER-*-\r\n\r\n1.It would be preferable if prior notice of at least 10 days would be given before the Performance Date.\r\n\r\n2.The Sound System should be as per the requirements of the band.\r\n\r\n3.A Memorandum Of Understanding (MoU) would be signed between both the parties, ie, The Band and the Contacting Party before the performance, which will include the total sum to be paid to The Band, in written along with signatures of both the parties.\r\n\r\n4.50% of the entire remuneration should be paid at the time of signing the MoU and the remaining 50% should be paid on the date of the performance before the band gets on stage to perform. These terms would be stated in the MoU.\r\n\r\n5.If the Performance is Cancelled due to any reason by the party engaging the band, then the entire amount taken in advance would be forfeited. If the band cancels the performance, then the advance would be returned.\r\n\r\nThe fan page links of the band are:\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\nhttp://www.reverbnation.com/lafzedilli\r\n\r\nhttps://www.facebook.com/lafzedilli\r\n\r\n\r\nP.S- WE NEED YOUR LOVE AND KEEP ROCKING WITH LAFZ-e-DILLI !!!!!!!!!!!!\r\nBand Interests\r\nLive Performances, Original Compositions.... Band members love to travel and perform in different cities.... Also looking forward for the in','9990630820(Md.Khalid),7503228680(Hayat),09811250513(Ashish) ','http://www.facebook.com/lafzedilli','http://www.reverbnation.com/lafzedilli','','http://www.reverbnation.com/lafzedilli','150797604990028','2069',0,NULL,NULL,'2012-09-06 07:27:31','2012-09-06 07:27:31',0,'','','lafz-the-band'),(417,0,4,4,'Nasik Rock Association -','Nasik Rock Association finally formed on 21st March 2010.All Bands came together and took a decision in order to change the Rock Scenario in Nasik.We have formed this association for all those people who can help rock Bands from Nasik to flourish more n more......and get gigs in Nasik as well as outside Nasik.All the Bands in Nasik of every genre come under NRA.NRA will support every band and promote every band in the city to develop.All the \"METAL HEADS \" and ROCK LOVERS ALSO INVITED TO JOIN THIS PAGE...................PLEASE SHOW YOUR SUPPORT ','','http://www.facebook.com/nasik.rock.association','','','','110534375629941','2068',0,NULL,NULL,'2012-09-06 07:27:31','2012-09-06 07:27:31',0,'','','nasik-rock-association'),(418,0,2,2,'Diabolic Lords','Diabolic Lords is a Heavy Metal act from nasik, Maharashtra, India formed in sept 2010. our primary aim is to spread metal culture here in our city and to promote other bands here .diabolic is derived from a latin word which can be explained as \'devilish\' . band believes in playing originals, as now band have 5 compositions to their name.','diaboliclords666@gmail.com','http://www.facebook.com/diaboliclords666','','','','0','2063',0,NULL,NULL,'2012-09-06 07:27:31','2012-09-06 07:27:31',0,'','','diabolic-lords'),(419,0,88,88,'Moog Conspiracy','Head of the label Elektrotribe and successful electronic music producer, Moog Conspiracy has a tough\r\ndiscography including more than 40 tracks and a studio album. In only 3 years he has became one of the\r\nmost demanded Act in Europe, acclaimed for the amazing intensity & diversity of his dj and live\r\nperformances.\r\n\r\nIn 2010, the launch of Elektrotribe INTENSE Tour gives him the opportunity to play around the globe (USA /\r\nIndia ), playing either live or dj & special back to back sets with Elektrotribe artists like Breger, Animaltek or\r\nJalebee Cartel.\r\n\r\nMoog Conspiracy studio work is in big progress : his second studioalbum in expected for the first half of\r\n2011, and his newest productions are receiving the support of Richie Hawtin, Laurent Garnier, Luciano,\r\nRicardo Villalobos, Loco Dice, Audiofly, Oxia, Tocadisco, Eric Morillo, Someone Else, Max Cooper\r\n\r\nBIOGRAPHY ::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::\r\n\r\nMoog Conspiracy began his experimentations with music a long time ago. Since ten years with his metal roots, he walks on the path of constant improvement. Rock, trip-hop, minimal, funk, house, trance; his eager ears find sounds everywhere in order to create tomorrows ones.\r\n\r\nSo, how to qualify his music?... Always really deep and dark, he removes the hearts and souls with his minimalist electro. A strong techno beat, precise and acute; serpentine synthesizer melodies; a hate of obvious structures; destabilising noises: all an atmosphere that he creates, to make the listener rise from ecstatic heights to the black depths of human spirit.\r\n\r\nHis first EP began the legend. Is it deep? seduced a huge amount of techno freaks and DJs, like Lucio and Pep and Digital Filth who remixed his tracks, or Cosmopolitan who wanted him to remix for them. Now hes on the edge of another acid revolution with his new album \"Elements of Density\".\r\n\r\nMore than a DJ, hes a real creator, a true artist with a vision and a goal: transform music and let hearts shake.\r\n\r\nDISCOGRAPHY ::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::\r\n\r\nRELEASES ///\r\nMoog Conspiracy & Breger  Screenshot (Elektrotribe) (2010)\r\nMoog Conspira