th album.','','http://www.facebook.com/ShadesOfRetribution','','','','100534056686237','1431',0,NULL,NULL,'2012-09-06 07:27:31','2012-09-06 07:27:31',0,'','','shades-of-retribution'),(532,0,0,0,'4 Degrees of Freedom','4 Degrees of Freedom started out with the name Disturbed in the autumn of 2006, playing simple rock and a bit of funk and trying to bring a change in the metal crazy crowd of Ranchi. Now, at present we are a band that can be proud of bringing funk & punk rock in Jharkhand inspired by the music of bands like Rage against the Machine, Sum 41 and Red Hot Chilli Peppers. Captivating a majority of the crowd, Hindi music lovers to groove to our funk we have been winning almost every rock competition in our State. \r\nIn our five years of existence together we have refined our music, thinking and our band name has evolved with it. In 2008 we changed our name to Morellos Mosh Pit only playing covers of RATM. Over the years as we got deeper into the music Tom Morello and the leftist philosophy of Zack de la Rocha. Here, we found something we could relate too, given the standing problems of the people of our very own state.\r\nToday, 4 Degrees of Freedom, is trying to convey what we feel and see through our music. Our music is for people to have fun but our lyrics to make them feel our thoughts .Our thoughts, for everyone to think a little more than, of what, they only see. We stand for a change. \r\nA pen, our minds, our music, these are our weapons of change. ','Zubin Ekka 08235012598/0657-6541819, zubinekka@gmail.com','http://www.facebook.com/FourDegreesofFreedom','','','','257540590954545','1429',0,NULL,NULL,'2012-09-06 07:27:31','2012-09-06 07:27:31',0,'','','4-degrees-of-freedom'),(533,0,0,0,'Calcutta blues','In THe Year 2005 CalcuTTa Blues  Was Established  The inception Of this Band Was By a Small Group of Youngman, Within a Span Of A Very Short Time It Has Gained Heart Of The Young Generation  And  Has Developed Their Rank In The Field Of Bangla Bands .