be to make music that they themselves enjoy, as well as the people outside the band can enjoy. \n\n\n','','http://www.facebook.com/mutinyinmarch','','','','179997842070266','1168',0,NULL,NULL,'2012-09-06 07:27:31','2012-09-06 07:27:31',0,'','','mutiny-in-march'),(599,0,0,0,'Big Bang Blues','Live Collaborations (Individually and as a band): \n\nJohn Ko (Babylon Extension) , Mama (East India Company), Abhinav Dhar, Toto (Stitch), Out of the Blue, Cross Fingers, Kozmic Blindz, Outdated, Vyaktam, Krossbreed, Orange Street, Tatva, Rusty Mystery, Sophie Annan, HeadsnTails and many more...\n\nKey Performances (Amongst many others):\n\nBlue Frog (Mumbai)\nHigh Spirits (Pune)\nBahi (Gurgaon)\nThe Living Room (Delhi)\nManajsa (Delhi)\nHaze (Delhi)\nCaf Morrison (Delhi)\nTurquoise Cottage (Delhi)\nESCAPE music festival (Naukuchiataal)\nWills India Fashion Week (Delhi)\nCommon Wealth Games - Youth Festival (Delhi) \nBreakfast Jam (HIT 95 FM)\n','bigbangblues@wishbone.in','http://www.facebook.com/bigbangblues','','','','146790139494','1159',0,NULL,NULL,'2012-09-06 07:27:31','2012-09-06 07:27:31',0,'','','big-bang-blues'),(600,0,0,0,'Harvester','Form in early 1992 by founding members Andy & Peter, the duo begin to recruit the early members of harvester to play their own infuse style of blackened melodic death metal/dark metal.\n\nThe band manage to release a full length album recorded at TNT in 1995. Titled \"..as we reap the fields of pain\" under Masterpiece Production.\n\nThat year also see the departure of some of our members and shuffling of the members.\n\nThe band take an extended hiatus when Peter left for Canada.\n\n12 years after the band hiatus. 2010, Harvester now return with partial original members to spread their own musical onslaught and are now preparing for the next 2nd full length album.','andy@thylordharvester.com','http://www.facebook.com/Harvestersg','','','','109837199040670','1158',0,NULL,NULL,'2012-09-06 07:27:31','2012-09-06 07:27:31',0,'','','harvester'