7 ','http://www.facebook.com/pages/Attyachari/255165917831665','','','','255165917831665','605',0,NULL,NULL,'2012-09-06 07:27:31','2012-09-06 07:27:31',0,'','','attyachari'),(815,0,0,0,'Arquebus','','arquebusindia@gmail.com','http://www.facebook.com/ArquebusBand','','','','200308176716291','602',0,NULL,NULL,'2012-09-06 07:27:31','2012-09-06 07:27:31',0,'','','arquebus'),(816,0,1,1,'DJ MoCity','DJ MoCity was Born In Baghdad Raised In New Delhi. This rising star DJ/MC/promoter/street artist has long held a reputation as Delhi nightlifes busiest man-about-town. Known nation-wide for his work with Reggae Rajahs, not to mention his earliest forays into event promotion with his legendary South Delhi Block parties, and numerous wildly popular properties he\'s been involved with such as Delitronica, Bass Camp & Holi Cow amongst others...\r\n\r\nThe Future (Monthly Night):\r\nAbout two years ago we stumbled upon fresh new sounds that needed to be shared with all of you. Therefore we set up a monthly night called The Future, where we showcase our selection from musical visionaries such as Gramatik, Michael Menert and of course, the artist who started it all, Pretty Lights. With the right combination of lights, sound and unexplored musical territory, we hope to inspire and spark a new path to our own Future.','mo@oml.in','http://www.facebook.com/Th3Future?ref=ts','http://www.djmocity.com','http://soundcloud.com/djmocity','','0','601',0,NULL,NULL,'2012-09-06 07:27:31','2012-09-06 07:27:31',0,'','','dj-mocity'),(817,0,0,0,'Cobweb','The Band Formed: 1992\n\nBand Members:\nSiddartha Dhakhwa - Drums\nNilesh Joshi - Bass\nRohit Banmali -Guitar + Vocals\nDibesh Mulmi - Guitar + Vocals\nSunil Shakya - Guitar + Vocals\nSandeep - Sound Setup\n\nBand formed: 1992\n\nTotal Albums: Seven\n\nName of Albums:\nAnjaan (1993)\nCobweb (1996)\nRollin String (1998)\nMercedes Benz (2000)\nRock n Roll (2002)\nSwing (2004)\nNamaste (2010)\n\nAwards:\nSajjan Smiriti Competition (1996) - Award for Best