ted in 1999 at the age of 15, Vanshi has had the distinct advantage of early experience. The DJ-ing scenario was still evolving when he began learning his way around the console. He grew with the industry, crossing milestones along the way and establishing himself as a Pro Music Producer in a matter of years.\nHe specializes in Lounge, World Music and House catering to a vast segment of the audience.\nVanshi started out in his hometown Hyderabad. After his initial training, he moved to Mumbai, where he taught music production And DJing to aspiring DJs at one of Indias most sought-after DJs , DJ Nashas Workstation.\nAt the famous Mood Indigo festival of IIT Powai, Vanshi was adjudged 1st Runner Up in the All India War of DJs.\nHaving gained ample experience in Mumbai, he moved to Bangalore, the leading party capital of India.\nVanshi developed his skills playing at numerous parties, private bashes, celebrity dos and at various pubs and nightclubs. His star-studded list of clientele include  Shefali Zariwala, Actor Madhavan and the whos who of Bangalore.\nOne of his biggest landmarks came in 2007 when he was ranked 2ndRunner Up at the Times War of DJs  National Finals.\nVanshi is currently Resident DJ at the Olive Beach & Ice Bar, Vivanta by Taj, at Bangalore. Catch him spinning his new mixes at these popular hot-spots.\nArmed with experience, young age and tremendous reserves of energy, Vanshi is on the fast track to being one of the most sought after DJs and Music Producers.\n','','http://www.facebook.com/DJVanshi','','','','108239319264915','571',0,NULL,NULL,'2012-09-06 07:27:31','2012-09-06 07:27:31',0,'','','dj-vanshi'),(830,0,0,0,'Khiladi','refer website','','http://www.facebook.com/pages/Khiladi/145664435484475','','','','145664435484475','571',0,NULL,NULL,'2012-09-06 07:27:31','2012-09-06 07:27:31',0,'','','khiladi'),(831,0,0,0,'Iterate','Leaving stains on your bedsheets since September, 2011; working on debut EP to be out soon. Winners of Dhwani(COE, Trivandr