m'),(905,0,0,0,'Inside 2 Stoopid Triangles','We got together in 2002 with the sole intention of pissing you off while playing some mean punk rock.  You can have a sigh of relief, unlock your doors and let your daughters and wives out now since we\'ve stopped raiding villages and are no longer active.\n\n\"But why a band page for a band that isn\'t even around?\" you might ask. A fist to your face might be the proper answer but we\'re all older so we\'ll refrain from violence. To be honest (when weren\'t we?), think of this page as a joint for four bitter old fucks desperately clinging on to dead memories, unable to cope with the responsibilities of adult life. Or because Geocities closed shop taking our awesome website down with them and we were a band that always had a web presence. The choice is yours.\n\nUpdate - Baam, Lambu and Kai (along with Ranav of Cruentus) today play in the largely inactive hardcore band Jugaa while Dhobi plays guitar in the NYC based Nepali hardcore band Sangharsha.\n\nJugaa - http://www.facebook.com/pages/Jugaa/51344200867\n\nSangharsha - http://www.facebook.com/pages/Sangharsha/331253598544','','http://www.facebook.com/inside2stoopidtriangles','','','','346423407048','472',0,NULL,NULL,'2012-09-06 07:27:31','2012-09-06 07:27:31',0,'','','inside-2-stoopid-triangles'),(906,0,0,0,'Stigma (India)','','Anchal Bhargava- 09893367540,Prakash raj Misha-09755008725','http://www.facebook.com/pages/Stigma-India/223197251032771','','','','223197251032771','471',0,NULL,NULL,'2012-09-06 07:27:31','2012-09-06 07:27:31',0,'','','stigma-india'),(908,0,0,0,'Genetic IdiotS','\nKarry  : Lead guitarist/plucking\nAkash : Rhythm guitars/vocals\nShaurya : vocals/screams/Keyboard\n','','http://www.facebook.com/genetic.idiots','','','','201004093282947','466',0,NULL,NULL,'2012-09-06 07:27:31','2012-09-06 07:27:31',0,'','','genetic-idiots'),(909,0,0,0,'Jeepers Creepers','Jeepers Creepers was formed in 2011 with an effort to break away from the conventions,trying to