w months,Pratiq appointed Vipin on bass and Gaurav on drums.\nAs a band,their main concentration is to make good melodies and then give it a groove with Guitars and Vocals.\n      ','+91 9878509007','http://www.facebook.com/pages/Aarzoo-the-BAND/185354124854765','','','','185354124854765','439',0,NULL,NULL,'2012-09-06 07:27:31','2012-09-06 07:27:31',0,'','','aarzoo-the-band'),(928,0,0,0,'Moonburn','','','http://www.facebook.com/moonburn666','','','','156543724430880','439',0,NULL,NULL,'2012-09-06 07:27:31','2012-09-06 07:27:31',0,'','','moonburn'),(929,0,1,1,'DJ MAKI','','077 4949 433','http://www.facebook.com/DEEJMAKI','','','','192256680822715','435',0,NULL,NULL,'2012-09-06 07:27:31','2012-09-06 07:27:31',0,'','','dj-maki'),(930,0,0,0,'Propeller heads','','','http://www.facebook.com/pages/Propeller-heads/111962725495863','','','','111962725495863','434',0,NULL,NULL,'2012-09-06 07:27:31','2012-09-06 07:27:31',0,'','','propeller-heads'),(931,0,0,0,'White City','White City are Andronik on drums/keyboards/BVs, Ru on vox/bass, Travka on guitar/sounds and Archie on sounds/noise/guitars \n\nThey met in Kabul. They started making noise. ','whitecity@biginthstans.com','http://www.facebook.com/whitecitykabul','','','','207860175892390','434',0,NULL,NULL,'2012-09-06 07:27:31','2012-09-06 07:27:31',0,'','','white-city'),(932,0,0,0,'11thHour','11th Hour started out in 2007,with founding members being Aron,Meban,Banbit,who are still with the current line up.The band added Joey(Scream Of Silence,Bangalore)to its line up a year later,with the latest addition being Aris/Paul,on drums who replaced Jonah.Due to obstacles and committment issues,Meban(Founder guitarist)has left the band and has been replaced by Criss.The bands shows include-\n\n1) Mawlai Beat Contest,Mawlai-2007(Winners)\n2)Return of Rock Warriors,Amlarem-2008\n3)New Year\'s Moshpit,Shillong-2008\n4)Nagaland Youth Fest.Kohima-2009\n5)Reigning Death,Shillong-2009(Headlining Act)\n6)Mawngap New Years Bash,Mawngap-2009(H