e Metal band that was formed in early June 2011, originating from Nugegoda, Sri Lanka. \n\nRavenSung consisted of six school mates who loved and were deeply moved by the Progressive/Heavy/Thrash/Melodic genre. As time passed by, the band experimented on their music; moving from Heavy/Melodic music to the current Progressive Metal genre. \n\nWhile the band were developing and honing their skills and integrity, Supun had to leave the country in order to pursue his studies. Akila filled his spot as the current Lead guitarist, while Lalinda filled in for Rhythm. Soon Dimitri joined to fill Selaka\'s place in Bass, while Dhyresh took charge of lead vocals and Gayan continued on drums. \n\nRavenSung performed their first and successful major gig at Ominous Gathering : Testament II which was held recently this year. ','','http://www.facebook.com/pages/RavenSung/222504797778179','','','','222504797778179','302',0,NULL,NULL,'2012-09-06 07:27:31','2012-09-06 07:27:31',0,'','','ravensung'),(1046,0,0,0,'Gaida Taskar','Gaida Taskar was formed in late 2007 by Sarthak the concept of band,name and music was therefore decided by he himself.With the lineup( Wabun,Dipesh.Bikash and Sarthak) but the band did\'nt worked as it was planned.After a year Biplop,Dipesh,Suman and Bikash(2008) started the band with the motive of playing punk music,ups and down came too much in the band,genre clash became the biggest problem.Seneth started band at 2010 replacing Biplop and again at 2011 Biplop replaced Seneth.At the current phase Gaida Taskar is playing hardcore music with no rules of any musical genre.Current line up Salil,Suman,Seneth,Bikash and Biplop.(2011)','9803965832,9841386715','http://www.facebook.com/pages/Gaida-Taskar/70913059839','','','','70913059839','301',0,NULL,NULL,'2012-09-06 07:27:31','2012-09-06 07:27:31',0,'','','gaida-taskar'),(1047,0,0,0,'Haemorrhage','','','http://www.facebook.com/pages/Haemorrhage/228423347225909','','','','228423347225909','301',0,NULL,NULL,'2012-09-06 07:27:31','2012-09-06 07:27:31',0,'','','haemorrhage'),(1048,0,0,0,'Fusion XxXtract','\"Fusion XxXtract\" is a  journey of 5 Indian men who picked up instruments n walked into something \"confined\" as a rock band and yet sound like the amalgamation of the western influences with ethnic Indian roots in the melting pot of the cosmic powers in the universe and deliver it in the form of musical notes,with languages not a barrier policy.The members truly believe in the power of music and create a breath-taking positive vibe with soul-renderring and energetic performance.The bands music reflects this very sentiment.The members have played all over Mumbai at lounges and inter-college festivals and classical concerts,individually but however as a band,they have concentrated on their music, and are yet to be regulars at big venues as the \"Fusion XxXtract\".\n\nAchievements:-\n\n    * \'Fusion XxXtract\' earned critical as well as audience\' acclaim as the most versatile band for Malhars Got Talent(MGT) 2010(For having performed in 4 languages-Bengali,Hindi,Malayalam,Kannada).\n    * \'Fusion XxXtract\' also won II Runner Up in the English Band event at Kaleidoscope 2010.\n     *Placed 4th among 30 Mumbai & out-station bands for Mantra(Mood Indigo-Asias largest Inter-College Cultural Festival )\n\nIn a very short period of time since the inception of the band \"Fusion XxXtract\" has managed to make quite a furore among the college bands circuit after winning the english band event @ Kaleidoscope 2010 & performing for the finals of the band events for Umang 2010(Hindi), Malhar 2010(English) & Mood Indigo 2010(Hindi) & enthralling the audiences with rocking and full-power performance.\n\n\n\n','fusion.xtract@gmail.com','http://www.facebook.com/pages/Fusion-XxXtract/142771665777482','','','','142771665777482','300',0,NULL,NULL,'2012-09-06 07:27:31','2012-09-06 07:27:31',0,'','','fusion-xxxtract'),(1049,0,0,0,'Anti-Trust (Nagaland)','We are 4 play HeavyMetal band based from Kohima (Nagaland).','','http://www.facebook.com/pages/Anti-Trust-Nagaland/206132332792623','','','','206132332792623','299',0,NULL,NULL,'2012-09-06 07:27:31','2012-09-06 07:27:31',0,'','','anti-trust-nagaland'),(1050,0,0,0,'BlueOrb / BuffaPirate','\"And then there was the music, the beautiful music! ...but in Prakeths hands he turned those songs into a narrative and an emotional journey! - SolipsisticNation\"\r\n\r\nblueOrb\'s sets present a eclectic view into the plethora of exquisite electronic music, creating a cohesive blend of spacy ambient, intricate mid-tempo beats to high energy dancefloor grooves.\r\n\r\nblueOrb is Praketh Sunder. Conceptualized in 2004 he has been a driving force in promoting and spinning electronic chillout at various music events in India, while further expanding his style towards the dancefloor in 2007. \r\n\r\nbuffaPirate is his alter ego to plunder a unique take on bass heavy electronic music. His sets can best be described as an amalgamation of west coast glitch-hop, reggae/hip-hop infused dubstep, big room breaks along with funk driven fidget-bassline house. His sets always keep the dance floor on its toes with surprises lurking at every junction & have drawn a positive response across a varied audience.\r\n\r\nPraketh is the Label DJ for Audio Aashram (IN) & Bassweight Recordings (NZ). He has also compiled 2 chillout EP\'s titled \"Shanti Broadcast Vol 1 & 2\" for Audio Aashram which are available on beatport.com.\r\n\r\nStay tuned for more exciting news!','','http://www.facebook.com/blueorbindia','','','','145988938807567','297',0,NULL,NULL,'2012-09-06 07:27:31','2012-09-06 07:27:31',0,'','','blueorb-buffapirate'),(1051,0,0,0,'Jonas Desai','Jonas Desai was born on the 18th of February 1986 in Skellefte, Sweden. He is the youngest child in a family of 5 to a Swedish Mother and an Indian father. Music has always been a part of Jonas\' life. In the early days however, \"jam sessions\" with his brothers often took the backseat in favour of his other great love, Football. Jonas truly realized his musical passion when he picked up a guitar for the first time in 2002. He quickly mastered the guitar and started fine-tuning and shaping his voice to the characteristic yet versatile style of singing that we enjoy today. The first single Get Me Out from the album A Weight Off My Mind was written in Sweden during 2006. \nJonas Get Me Out came true in 2007 when he was approached by producer Reiner Erlings and signed by Involved Music, Dubai. Jonas moved to Dubai to pursue his professional music career.\n\nDesai opened for Jesse Cook, David Gray and Robin Gibb at the Dubai International Jazz Festival in Feb 2008 shortly after releasing his first EP \'Get me out\' through Involved Music. After spending the rest of the year in the studio, Jonas\' debut album A Weight Off My Mind was successfully launched in the Middle East at the end of December 2008. In reviews of A Weight Off My Mind Jonas has been compared to a young John Mayer.\n2009 started at a high pace where some of the highlights were the headline spots at Dubai Tennis Championship Official Players party and The Slobfest in Dubai as well as the visit to his fans in India with a gig at the renowned Blue Frog, Mumbai. Jonas will be performing in and around the Middle East during spring as he prepares for launch and release in Scandinavia summer -09.\n','Andreas Desai','http://www.facebook.com/pages/Jonas-Desai/24667211256','','','','24667211256','296',0,NULL,NULL,'2012-09-06 07:27:31','2012-09-06 07:27:31',0,'','','jonas-desai'),(1052,0,0,0,'Solitary Souls','Have played in selected contests and have won most of them but performing live on a good platform is always the best thing...','07797918435','http://www.facebook.com/pages/Solitary-Souls/139479882767393','','','','139479882767393','296',0,NULL,NULL,'2012-09-06 07:27:31','2012-09-06 07:27:31',0,'','','solitary-souls'),(1053,0,0,0,'Zowe Madrigal','The only Neo-Classical male voice group in the country. Started in October 2009 with a vision to promote music of different genres. Zowe Madrigal is led by Nise Meruno.The Group consists of people from varied background but strong and dedicated people. After its inception, the group has been invited to perform for a number of shows,concerts and weddings., Viz, A Night At The Broadway (First Concert), Hornbill Festival 2009.2010..etc..Zowe Madrigal biggest achievement till date would be the opportunity to perform for The President of India in Dec 2009 and Dec 2010 at The Rashtrapati Bhavan. They were well received by the audience as well as the media. Some of the members also had the privilege to perform for the third time during The President\'s maiden visit to Nagaland 2011. Zowe Madrigal led by Nise Meruno recently gave a successful concert in Guwahati under the aegis of Yamaha Music company. They also performed in Delhi at the India Habitat Centre and The Neemrana Fort Palace in June 2011. Zowe Madrigal had the privilege to perform with French Dancer/Choreographer Gilles Chuyen and India\'s best known Soprano Situ Singh Buehler. The Concert tour was supported by the Neemrana Music Foundation and Kawai Grand Piano company. Zowe Madrigal repertoire includes Western Classical, Sacred, Jazz, Contemporary, Popular Classics, Bollywood,. etc..However the Group\'s forte lies in Naga Folk Fusion originals. Mostly arranged and composed by The Director Nise Meruno.   ','madrigalyoho@gmail.com','http://www.facebook.com/pages/Zowe-Madrigal/244948032190603','','','','244948032190603','294',0,NULL,NULL,'2012-09-06 07:27:31','2012-09-06 07:27:31',0,'','','zowe-madrigal'),(1054,0,0,0,'4 Strings Apart','Four friends get together to do what they do best.make music :)','','http://www.facebook.com/4StringsApart','','','','204154309629549','292',0,NULL,NULL,'2012-09-06 07:27:31','2012-09-06 07:27:31',0,'','','4-strings-apart'),(1055,0,0,0,'Atext','','','http://www.facebook.com/pages/Atext/248604585176945','','','','248604585176945','291',0,NULL,NULL,'2012-09-06 07:27:31','2012-09-06 07:27:31',0,'','','atext'),(1056,0,0,0,'Khancoban','Two albums and a mini album. From Melbourne.\n\nkhancoban make gorgeously slow burn records, treading the under-represented line between a kind of folk beauty and the excitement of out-and-out rock \'n\' roll noise. They\'ve been compared to Arcade Fire, Wilco and Augie March, which is correct as far as those sorts of things are concerned but doesn\'t go nearly far enough in telling the full story of the complexity and inherent value in this amazing band.\n\nTony McMahon, Inpress.','','http://www.facebook.com/khancoban.band','','','','17852571886','288',0,NULL,NULL,'2012-09-06 07:27:31','2012-09-06 07:27:31',0,'','','khancoban'),(1057,0,0,0,'Karma (India)','It all started in 2010 when, seeking a break from the monotony of a day spent in class, choral singers Arjun and Ritvik joined their college acoustic team. Sharing a similar taste and appreciation for the music of yesteryears led to after-college jams which they hoped would be reproduced on stage. \n\nUnfortunately, this was not to be. \n\nThey decided to move on to bigger and better.\n\nA year later, things suddenly fell into place. Having recruited Savio, an enthusiastic drummer known for his windfall monetary earnings and Nitin, a skilled musician who simply fancied a go at the lead guitar, the band was complete with the addition of Neil, a bassist and sound-engineer looking to play something a little more mellow.\n\nKarma\'s choice of genre has found universal appeal in Bangalore, with the band getting calls to play at several venues all over the city.\n\n\n\n','','http://www.facebook.com/pages/Karma-India/103337293075164','','','','103337293075164','286',0,NULL,NULL,'2012-09-06 07:27:31','2012-09-06 07:27:31',0,'','','karma-india'),(1058,0,0,0,'HFT','HFT play a style of music that could easily be called world jazz, jazz that is urbane and savvy, a well-travelled, warm music that is equally at ease being in the sun as resting in the shade. \n\nAJmellifluous melody line maker on the guitar and sometime scatman in a hat, Lewfunky bass line plucker and creator of psychedelia in song, and Suchetseated beatkeeper on drums from as far afield as Peru and Uganda, make up this trio. \n\nInfluences for the band range from Miles Davis to Baaba Maal. Listening to them live, youd hear jazz through the guitar melodies, bass runs & cymbals, fusion through the raga-esque phrasing and scat, world music in the Afrobeat drum grooves \n\nDrawing inspiration from everywhere, HFTs music speaks of the here and now. Music as it is, sounding the best it can.','','http://www.facebook.com/hftmusicindia','','','','172845989425536','286',0,NULL,NULL,'2012-09-06 07:27:31','2012-09-06 07:27:31',0,'','','hft-1'),(1059,0,0,0,'Sandeep Chowta Projects','','','http://www.facebook.com/pages/Sandeep-Chowta-Projects/225677834114202','','','','225677834114202','285',0,NULL,NULL,'2012-09-06 07:27:31','2012-09-06 07:27:31',0,'','','sandeep-chowta-projects'),(1060,0,0,0,'Two-Piece','','','http://www.facebook.com/piecetwo','','','','308143049213100','285',0,NULL,NULL,'2012-09-06 07:27:31','2012-09-06 07:27:31',0,'','','two-piece'),(1061,0,0,0,'Samay Yantra','','','http://www.facebook.com/Samay.Yantra','','','','172757942801888','284',0,NULL,NULL,'2012-09-06 07:27:31','2012-09-06 07:27:31',0,'','','samay-yantra'),(1062,0,0,0,'Indra J','Indra J (Founder and ex-member Grahan Chronicles) saw the future of EDM and brought it to people in Gujarat, India, who did not have access to it almost alongwith the global growth of the genre and is one of the prime forces behind the promotion of Edm there. \n\nIndra J always has had his own thing, played his own music to sold out venues,from closing sets for the Trance legends such as Simon Posford to performing for 5000 people in festivals, this man has done it all in his 8 year long career.\n\nHe was recognized and interviewed by India Today amongst the top 3 underground Djs of Gujarat along with Bandish Projekt and Nukleya and also selected for the young entrepreneurship award by the Yourstory.in.\nHe has had several Progressive house/Trance releases  on Chill Om Records under his act Grahan Chronicles ,some of which have been supported by  Radio stations all over the world including Bobby friction on BBC Radio 1, GLobal Dj Broadcast, DJ Tarkan, Suffused, Hypnotic Duo, Moshic,etc. \n\nIndra J also has a regular Monthly Show \'Disco Fantasy\' on Insomnia Fm, first monday of every month.\n ','','http://www.facebook.com/Indrajofficial','','','','135952263129953','283',0,NULL,NULL,'2012-09-06 07:27:31','2012-09-06 07:27:31',0,'','','indra-j'),(1063,0,0,0,'Arms Of Silence','','09862372979, 09774339260, 09774006659','http://www.facebook.com/thearmsofsilence','','','','159554310764654','281',0,NULL,NULL,'2012-09-06 07:27:31','2012-09-06 07:27:31',0,'','','arms-of-silence'),(1064,0,0,0,'Tushar Sachdeva ( Anchor/ Singer/ Composer)','Recognised as a new sensation in the music industry Proprieter of SME,Manager and Vocalist of rock band HEAVEN BROTHERS , anchor of band DREAMERS, over a decade of experience and expertise of performing live and captivating the hearts of the listenershaving links with the major bands of the nation like PARIKRAMA, INDAIN OCEANS, EUFORIA , EKA , BANDISH, GAURAV AND SIMON UNCLE, etc .... is also persuing his graduation from BVIMR for Computer Applications and inspite of all this music , manages to take out time to work for and with this reputed institution. Taking keen interest in making this first live project after completeing a 3 months internship	in MTNL Ltd. under the Computer Networking Section\n\nHISTORY\n\n...Born on 17th December 1990, Tushar Sachdeva, is a true Musician at heart. Equipped with Skills and an Experience of more than \'10 years of Performing\' across the Nation and living up everytime to the expectations of all his listeners and viewers, he managed to know his targeted audience well, and tries to cover every type of musical genre to entertain and rejuvenate one\'s soul.\nPRESENT\n\n1. Owns his own Music Tutorials by the name of \"SACH MUSIC ENTERTAINMENT (S.M.E.)\" \n2. Working as the Manager for last 2 years under \" SACH SEWA GROUP (S.S.G) \" which recently completed its 5th year of successful existence.\n\n3. Owns a techno-rock band by the name \"THE HEAVEN BROTHERS\" which regularly performs in various places in and across delhi. Visit \"http://heavenbrothers.blogspot.com/\" for more info.\n\n3. A part of few successful delhi based rock bands\n(A) RAHASYA RAAG (working as the Drummer)\n\n(B) THE DREAMERS (working as the Theme creator, Anchor, Distorted guitar & Backing Vocals)\n\n(C) MAYAJAAL (working as Drummer / Percussionist)\n','','http://www.facebook.com/TusharSachdeva.MyMusic','','','','161479127237257','280',0,NULL,NULL,'2012-09-06 07:27:31','2012-09-06 07:27:31',0,'','','tushar-sachdeva-anchor-singer-composer'),(1065,0,0,0,'Crossed Authority','','+9779813590480','http://www.facebook.com/pages/Crossed-Authority/183433111689857','','','','183433111689857','280',0,NULL,NULL,'2012-09-06 07:27:31','2012-09-06 07:27:31',0,'','','crossed-authority'),(1066,0,0,0,'Aikya','The members, after extensive training in Indian Classical music and long-term exposure to a wide variety of different musical genres, have found a common strength and an urge to combine their ideas and flourish collectively. Our favorite mode of expression is an aesthetic mix of the richness and flavor of Hindusthani classical music, combined with elements of rock and blues. This unique fusion enables us to speak our mind, channelize our individual musical sensibilities, and unite to make music of a different kind.','( +91-9874215874)','http://www.facebook.com/aikyamusic','','','','341349032574681','279',0,NULL,NULL,'2012-09-06 07:27:31','2012-09-06 07:27:31',0,'','','aikya'),(1067,0,0,0,'Bluetooth','','Rituparna Choudhury : 8486406526 ; Rishav Bhuyan : 9707431732 ; Sameer Baishnab : 986403