\nOur message to everyone is that Rock n roll is for life, Let it inside you, feel it, breathe it love it, live it, respect it, worship it, make the sacrifice. .. .then sharpen your skills n your gears of war. . Then next time in battle youll see that every strike u make, summons fire down from the depths of hell. . .\n And as for us, time has come for us to rise. And there shall be light.\n\npast performances:\ndelhi,mumbai,nagpur,noida,gurgaon,bangalore,etc.....','','http://www.facebook.com/pages/Analog-Machines/157777807591690','','','','157777807591690','274',0,NULL,NULL,'2012-09-06 07:27:31','2012-09-06 07:27:31',0,'','','analog-machines'),(1074,0,0,0,'Manifestator','Releases : \n2012 February 03 - Doom Over Live (Demo-Bootleg) http://www.mediafire.com/?6nd2hqfts1c6umz ','themanifestator@gmail.com','http://www.facebook.com/Manifestator','','','','261839847159534','271',0,NULL,NULL,'2012-09-06 07:27:31','2012-09-06 07:27:31',0,'','','manifestator'),(1075,0,0,0,'Death in My Dreams','Death conquers all........... and we depict this fact to all\nWe are the damn roots of this thing....We are the ones to start metal in our school....\\m/\nAnd,tired of all the usual hip hop and rock shit, that is prevalent all over we decided to form a metal band.When we were formed,we had literally no idea on music and had minimal experience on instruments,but that didnt stop us.We were there to give an impact and introduce metal to these guys.\"Death conquers all in the end\" and we were there to depict that fact through the messege of proper n brutal metal music....and thus the first metal band of DAV,Cspur was born....\n\\m/ DEATH IN MY DREAMS \\m/\nYeah,the road was tough and we had to face many obstacles,but we aint complaining...With every other war we earned a scar and with every new scar we earned respect,experience and skill.....no stopping now....\nWe r here to give u our best.We r here to introduce the darker side of life to you.We are.......DIMD..\nSTAY HARD...STAY METAL.