http://www.facebook.com/pages/RU-Rock-Unleashed/120008001362907','','','','120008001362907','221',0,NULL,NULL,'2012-09-06 07:27:31','2012-09-06 07:27:31',0,'','','ru-rock-unleashed'),(1107,0,0,0,'The Gig Bang Theory','Every once in a Morvet\'s comet or the rains on Magraetha, as the legend goes, four individuals with pre-synchronized electro-encephalo-waves gather to emanate such incredible ripples in the hertz field leaving those who witness the event with immensely satiated temporal lobe orgasms!! That\'s what The Gig Bang Theory does when they perform live! \nThe band members all of them who are docs in St. John\'s Medical college (except for Selvan who\'s an honorary Johnite :) met under various circumstances and various times, lets leave a certain amount of mystery which is always good.\nNevertheless, just as rare it is to find the perfect complimentary nucleotide strand to produce a Eric Johnson or a Joe Satriani; Richard, a Radiodiagnosis Post Grad student and Selvan, a Clinical Research professional, are two such guitarists who dwell and exploit the belief in being musicians free to express emotions only a few Earth bound soul have felt. Needless to add, Alex, an ENT surgeon, the man behind the skins and cymbals packs not only a powerful punch, but can make them lexicographers expand their definition of \'percussion\'. Last but not the least, Rahul, the new entry in the band under the apperenticeship of all the 3 above is a genuinely sweet final year Med student chappy and the bassist with stage antics to dwarf Flee!!!\nAnd last but most definitely not the least, The Gig Bang Theory has had the privilege and pleasure to have on board one of Bangalore\'s most sought after keyboardist, Rauf Abdul, from Ministry Of Blues fame. His presence exponentially augments the bands sound, bringing in a good balance of hammond tones and needless to say, a warmer sound.\n','','http://www.facebook.com/pages/The-Gig-Bang-Theory/126338437397645','','','','126338437397645','218',0,NULL,NULL,'2012-09-06 07:27:31','2012-09-06 07:27:31',0,'','','the-gig-bang-theory'),(1108,0,0,0,'Kixmet','KIXMET : metal as it\'s meant to be. Heart, soul and balls! \n\nWe\'re the only metal/rock band in India that has never played a single cover at any of our gigs. All Original, all the way!','00919822480663','http://www.facebook.com/pages/Kixmet/219245674765877','','','','219245674765877','218',0,NULL,NULL,'2012-09-06 07:27:31','2012-09-06 07:27:31',0,'','','kixmet'),(1109,0,0,0,'ReVerse OsmOsis','As the name suggests, means purification\n\n\nPurifying every soul with his music, Reverse Osmosis has come a long way in the Global music scene, Being Signed on Indias leading record label Chill Om Records and producing some superb Progressive Dance Music Tunes.\n\n\n\nThe wide Diversity in the music style has taken him to a different level altogether.\n\n\n\nA crazy blend of electronic & bouncey melodies with the sounds from the Electronic Universe has led him to gain support from the very best in the global electronic music market such as Hernan Catteno, Global Dj Broadcast, Dj Tarkan, Hypnotic Duo, TaTvA Kundalini, Moshic and a whole lot of more producers/Djs.\n\n\n\nWhere \"ReVerse OsmOsis\" is producing exclusive tunes that are being highly appreciated by artist from around the globe, he has also been slamming a lot of cites such as Bangalore, Goa, Jaipur etc.\n\n\n\nWith remixing world acclaimed artistes such as Robert K, TaTvA Kundalini to having several releases on various record stores such as Beatport, Itunes, Juno.\nHere\'s no denying ReVerse OsmOsis  has a great deal of  presence & drive but with his modest attitude its almost hard to believe he has accomplished so much in span of a year. Although its visually impossible you can literally just see what\'s next for this young hardworking trendsetter. If you are one of the few who are unfamiliar with ReVerse OsmOsis then he just might be another DJ for you but to his fans & supporters he is The \"reVerse OsmOsis\" a.k.a. the ultimate soul purifier, with his tantalizing music delivering ability and ever innovative skills to produce some great hits; entertaining and never leaving a fan unhappy! \n\nHe has entertained crowd and pulled \'em up on their feet at various gigs, Guys you just don\'t have to, but \"need\" to listen to many of his amazing feet tapping music. He is the next thing to be hitting the global scene with that \"brilliantly disturbing\" music of his, no wonder he is already creating some waves  - HE HAS ARRIVED!!!!!!\n\n\n\n\nReleases :\n\n	One Right Nite  Reverse Osmosis  Chill Om Records Beatport/Juno/Itunes\n\n	True Liez Ep  Reverse Osmosis  Chill Om Records  Beatport/Juno/Itunes\n\n	Kill The Bill Ep  Reverse Osmosis Remix  Chill Om Records  Beatport/Itunes/Juno\n\n	Sugar Gets Me Hi  Reverse Osmosis Remix  Chill Om Records Beatport/Itunes/Juno\n\n	Mughals Of The Taj  Reverse Osmosis Remix  Chill Om Records  Beatport/Itunes/Juno\n\n	Vibe Charger Ep  Reverse Osmosis - Chill Om Records  Beatport/Itunes/Juno\n\n	Life On a Knob Ep  Reverse Osmosis  Chill Om Records  Beatport/Itunes/Juno\n\n	Plush Ep  Reverse Osmosis Remix  Chill Om Records   Beatport/Itunes/Juno\n\n	Silence Ep  Reverse Osmosis Remix  Chill Om Records  Beatport/Itunes/Juno\n\n	Disco Fantasy Ep  Reverse Osmosis  Chill Om Records  Beatport/Itunes/Juno\n\n\nRadio Show Appearances :\n\n	Chill Om Urban Sessions - 91.1 fm Radio city, India\n\n	Sugar Gets Me Hi - Hosted by TaTvA K  Guest Reverse Osmosis\n\n	Pure Fm  Kundalini Rising  Hosted by TaTvA K  Guest  Reverse Osmosis','info@chillomrecordsindia.com','http://www.facebook.com/pages/ReVerse-OsmOsis/124342490981060','','','','124342490981060','216',0,NULL,NULL,'2012-09-06 07:27:31','2012-09-06 07:27:31',0,'','','reverse-osmosis'),(1110,0,0,0,'Origin East','','','http://www.facebook.com/origineast','','','','205036872879899','216',0,NULL,NULL,'2012-09-06 07:27:31','2012-09-06 07:27:31',0,'','','origin-east'),(1111,0,0,0,'Social Suicide','Social Suicide, a high energy rock cover band demanding their place in the music scene. They offer a huge variety of music to please any ear and any age group.  They have the sound, look, and live experience that will leave a lasting impression on even the most critical audience.  Be sure to come out and support Social Suicide at a venue near you!  ','','http://www.facebook.com/SocialSuicidePage','','','','154725534611499','212',0,NULL,NULL,'2012-09-06 07:27:31','2012-09-06 07:27:31',0,'','','social-suicide'),(1112,0,0,0,'The Escapades','','','http://www.facebook.com/pages/The-Escapades/178106602466','','','','178106602466','212',0,NULL,NULL,'2012-09-06 07:27:31','2012-09-06 07:27:31',0,'','','the-escapades'),(1113,0,0,0,'The Monkberries','Formed in March 2009 with a combination of various musicians with diverse backgrounds and musical exposure.\n\nEclectic is the word that comes to mind when trying to define the sound of Calcutta based band the Monkberries. A typical set list of the band includes songs from artists like The Eagles, Bo Bice, Linkin Park, Ben Harper, Poets of the Fall and Nil Langdrens Funk Unit just to name a few. The band also excels at giving old songs a new twist so that they sound relevant today just as they did back in the day.\n\nThis diverse genre of songs is due to the varied musical inclinations of the band members. Besides making for a unique listening experience, it also challenges the band members to learn different techniques, appreciate different styles and helps them grow as musicians. A lot of time is spent deciding upon the set list as the aim of the band is not only to entertain an audience but also open up new musical portals for the average listener.\n\nApart from doing covers the band has original compositions in the pipeline which it seeks to incorporate into their future playlists. As with the covers they do, the bands originals are guaranteed to vary in style and feel too. Although they are only a couple of shows old, the band has already begun to carve a niche for themselves in the music circuit. The band lives by the adage that practice makes perfect and have rolled up their sleeves and put their heads down to perfect their craft. As AC/DC aptly said Its a long way to the top if you wanna Rock n Roll! ','Kushal','http://www.facebook.com/pages/The-Monkberries/192866458570','','','','192866458570','211',0,NULL,NULL,'2012-09-06 07:27:31','2012-09-06 07:27:31',0,'','','the-monkberries'),(1114,0,0,0,'Nush Lewis','NushLewis is a contemporary Indian harpist trained at the KM Music Conservatory in Chennai. With three self-produced bedroom singles in the form of Blue Nails, Bright Orange Tea Cups and the appraised Shaair + Func mash-cover of Freeze You/ My Roots , her music is dominated by a feeling of darkness and surrealism. She is now focusing on bringing out a five track EP and looking to collaborate with more artists of various genres.\n\nP.S. I do not do wedding gigs !','','http://www.facebook.com/pages/Nush-Lewis/193890580709758','','','','193890580709758','209',0,NULL,NULL,'2012-09-06 07:27:31','2012-09-06 07:27:31',0,'','','nush-lewis'),(1115,0,0,0,'Mummypowder','Mummypowder are a 4-piece from Helsinki who\'ve released four albums in 12 years. The third album, \'Consternation! Uproar!\', besides being a critical success, was on Mtv rotation and was released in Japan. The 4th album will be released on May 11th 2011.','','http://www.facebook.com/pages/Mummypowder/32503079088','','','','32503079088','209',0,NULL,NULL,'2012-09-06 07:27:31','2012-09-06 07:27:31',0,'','','mummypowder'),(1116,0,0,0,'Heroin Slip','Heroin Slip is just another name for The P.A.G.E.','','http://www.facebook.com/pages/Heroin-Slip/158283917552489','','','','158283917552489','209',0,NULL,NULL,'2012-09-06 07:27:31','2012-09-06 07:27:31',0,'','','heroin-slip'),(1117,0,0,0,'Aditi Veena','','','http://www.facebook.com/AditiVeena','','','','213411598742466','209',0,NULL,NULL,'2012-09-06 07:27:31','2012-09-06 07:27:31',0,'