ll :-             +91 11 4444 7777      ','','','','www.mypurplemartini.com',NULL,NULL,'2012-09-06 07:27:33','2012-09-06 07:27:33',0,'','','','2012-07-12 10:05:00','1970-01-01 05:35:00','unplugged-night-with-agastya-band',1,NULL),(190,'ALTERNATIVE ROCK NIGHT With Thermal and a Quarter','ALTERNATIVE ROCK NIGHT With Thermal and a Quarter @ Blue Frog Delhi, Thermal And A Quarter (TAAQ) is a pioneering rock band from Bangalore. The band calls its music \'Bangalore Rock\', and makes a strong Indian connect even within the idiom of a \'Rock\' band. The TAAQ sound is open enough to accept Indian instruments and vocal stylings, and international enough to relate to global audiences. TAAQ has supported international acts like Deep Purple, Jethro Tull, Megadeth etc on tour in India; has completed tours in the UK, South-East Asia, Middle East. They recently toured the US and recorded their upcoming album, \"3 Wheels and 9 lives\" in New York. This album has been recorded and mixed live at New York by multiple Grammy Winner: Kirk Yano. Kirk is also known for his work with Miles Davis, Public Enemy & Mariah Carey.','','','','www.mypurplemartini.com',NULL,NULL,'2012-09-06 07:27:33','2012-09-06 07:27:33',0,'','','','2012-07-12 10:35:00','1970-01-01 05:35:00','alternative-rock-night-with-thermal-and-a-quarter',1,NULL),(191,'ROCK Night With Hundred Octane','ROCK Night With Hundred Octane @ Blue Frog Delhi, Rocking since 1995 and after several line up changes, this band is a revelation of sorts, an entity that is indestructible, invincible, irreversible, insatiable, inimitable, and has the sound of thunder and the days of metal. --hUndRed oCtaNe-- is a band that draws on PurpLe, Floyd, Soundgarden, STP, Pearl Jam, Alice In Chains, Led Zepplin...and yet remains uniquely spectacular. The rare quality of superb music writing stacked with matching lyrics and above all, fashioned with that deep thought provoking voice is what they are all about. MUSIC in MADNESS and MELODY in MAYHEM is what they believe in.','','','','www.mypurplemartini.com',NULL,NULL,'2012-09-06 07:27:33','2012-09-06 07:27:33',0,'','','','2012-07-12 09:35:00','1970-01-01 05:35:00','rock-night-with-hundred-octane',1,NULL),(193,'Bandish Projekt: Live Electronica','Bandish Projekt: Live Electronica @ Blue Frog Delhi Powered By www.mypurplemartini.com, About Bandish Projekt From the echo of festivals across India into the live energy of over numerous gigs, BANDISH PROJEKT has resounded in Dubai, Uk, Sweden, France, Amsterdam, Australia Played at Glastonbury, Edinburg Fringe Festival, Sommerszene festival (Austria), Melbourne Electronic Festival, Village India UK, Incubate festival, BBC Asian Network tour hasnt seemed to have captured enough of the BANDISH PROJEKT streak Since 2007. From Productions of Bollywood Films and documentaries, extraordinary club gigs, fusions and concerts for leading corporate houses to creation in drum n bass session tuning in to the best radio stations in India, Bandish Projekt seemed to be going anywhere that was everywhere! 2010 marks the year when BANDISH PROJEKT released its new album CORREKT and collaborates with the urbane performer to add new dimensions to its promising musical compendium. Also releases BROWN SKIN BEAUTY  New single from Bandish Projekt feat. Last Mango In Paris both on Bheja fry Records. The stage us all set for extraordinary cross-cultural music adventures, but its rots are firmly grounded to the passion of a crazy music fanatic! Mayur started dabbling in music at 2 and then trained in Indian classical music .A Tabla player, Mayur dived into exhilarating world percussion, earning repute as a tabla player, and adoration as a Jazz funk drummer. For More Info Call :-             +91 11 3080 0300       BB Pin :- 2945F1C4\r\n','','','','www.mypurplemartini.com',NULL,NULL,'2012-09-06 07:27:33','2012-09-06 07:27:33',0,'','','','2012-07-13 10:05:00','1970-01-01 05:35:00','bandish-projekt-live-electronica',1,NULL),(194,'Urban Early Men + Sk