ming of Benjamin Sequeira and the emotive lead-guitar bends and pulls by Douglas Misquita.\r\n\r\nComing together from a range of industries and influenced by The Rolling Stones, The Beatles, Elvis Presley, CCR and others of that genre, music is a serious pastime for this mix of doctors, businessmen, engineers, bankers, music instructors and media professionals - tempered in a cauldron of rigorous and regular practices and in-house music-critique; enough to make VICTOR AND THE CROWNS stand out as a much-awaited crowd-pulling act with their signature interpretations of a number of chart-toppers. Sing-along, scream-along, shake a leg, rock yourselves off your feet or just ENJOY!','','','','https://www.facebook.com/VictorandtheCrowns/info',NULL,NULL,'2012-09-06 07:27:33','2012-09-06 07:27:33',0,'','','','2012-08-05 09:05:00','1970-01-01 05:35:00','victor-and-the-crowns',1,NULL),(292,'Rum and Strings and Solder','','','https://www.facebook.com/events/453865687981552/','','https://www.facebook.com/events/453865687981552/',NULL,NULL,'2012-09-06 07:27:33','2012-09-06 07:27:33',0,'','','','2012-08-03 07:35:00','1970-01-01 05:35:00','rum-and-strings-and-solder',1,NULL),(337,'Strawberry Soul','','','','','http://nh7.in/gigs/strawberry-soul-at-counterculture/',NULL,NULL,'2012-09-06 07:27:33','2012-09-06 07:27:33',0,'','','','2012-08-03 08:35:00','1970-01-01 05:35:00','strawberry-soul',1,NULL),(340,'Supervibe at Hard Rock Cafe, Mumbai','','','','','http://nh7.in/gigs/supervibe-at-hard-rock-cafe-mumbai/',NULL,NULL,'2012-09-06 07:27:33','2012-09-06 07:27:33',0,'','','','2012-08-02 09:05:00','1970-01-01 05:35:00','supervibe-at-hard-rock-cafe-mumbai',1,NULL),(341,'Time Capsule','Time Capsule is a month long celebration of music, arts and culture both past and present. From intimate music to all- out rocking nights, Time Capsule aims to celebrate the works of some of the best artists, musicians and thinkers. From Syd Barrett of Pink Floyd to Chemical Brothers and Reggae Music, Augus