titled MotheredLand. Sunday, JUNE 3, 2012. \r\n\r\nThe lyrics for MotheredLand were penned by Shawn Pereira with music written by Anish Menon, Reinhart Dias, Roop Thomas, Shishir Thakur and Shawn Pereira. The album has been recorded and mixed at Yashraj studios by Shantanu Hudlikar (head Sound Engineer YRF) and Keshav Dhar (producer/songwriter Skyharbor). The album was mastered at Sterling Studios, New York by Chris Athens (Coldplay, AC/DC).  \r\n\r\n\'MotheredLand\' means a highly messed up state of affairs. It is our take on the current situation we find ourselves and our country in. The album seeks to point a finger at those responsible, and make people aware that sometimes we are just sheep in a game played, owned and run by wolves. The album cover and inlay was conceptualized by Blakc, designed by Elvin Pereira and illustrated by Sukrit Nagaraj and Vivek Nag. \r\n','','','','http://www.hardrockindiablog.com/',NULL,NULL,'2012-09-06 07:27:33','2012-09-06 07:27:33',0,'','','','2012-08-16 02:05:00','1970-01-01 05:35:00','blakc-live',1,NULL),(424,'Infusion Jazz','Infusion Jazz is a Bangalore based Jazz band comprising of Frijo Francis on Piano and Synth, Victor Francis on Drums and Dominic Yesudas on Acoustic Upright Bass and play a form of modern Jazz that cannot be called Avant-garde, but is definitely not in the classification of Dixieland or Be Bop .\r\n\r\n ','','','','http://eightoctaves.com/event/infusion-jazz-at-counterculture-bangalore/',NULL,NULL,'2012-09-06 07:27:33','2012-09-06 07:27:33',0,'','','','2012-08-13 08:35:00','1970-01-01 05:35:00','infusion-jazz',1,NULL),(425,'NEELIX + ANKYTRIXX ','One of the Biggest Nights of 2012! A night that will bring you face to face with two superpowers of Dance Music who have acquired PHDs in Destroying Dance Floors all across the Globe!','','','','http://www.bluefrog.co.in/events/neelix-ankytrixx',NULL,NULL,'2012-09-06 07:27:33','2012-09-06 07:27:33',0,'','','','2012-08-24 10:35:00','1970-01-01 05:35:00','neelix-ankyt