ock and Electronica. \r\n\r\nAman Mahajan is a pianist from the Berklee College of Music, Boston. He\'s worked with musicians from all over the world, playing music from jazz, blues and rock to electronica and Balinese gamelan.','http://www.reverbnation.com/show/8285148','http://www.facebook.com/events/307648775999861/','','http://www.facebook.com/events/307648775999861/',NULL,NULL,'2012-09-18 13:45:44','2012-09-18 13:45:44',0,'[\"\"]','[\"\"]','','2012-09-22 20:30:00','2012-09-22 23:00:00','the-radha-thomas-jazz-ensemble-at-bflat',1,NULL),(623,'DJ Rackish at Smoke House Grill','Get down, hood up and come with it every Wednesday, as Stone Water Grill is speakin in rhymes while DJ Rackish turns the tables with your favorite hip-hop mixes and takes you down the lane. Put your hands together and electrify them feet for the likes of Rihanna, T-Pain, Usher, Flo Rida, Jay-Z and Timbaland!','','','','http://nh7.in/gigs/dj-rackish-at-smoke-house-grill/',NULL,NULL,'2012-09-18 14:07:07','2012-09-18 14:07:07',0,'[\"\"]','[\"\"]','','2012-09-22 21:00:00','2012-09-22 23:30:00','dj-rackish-at-smoke-house-grill',1,NULL),(624,'Anil Chawla, Tuhin Mehta at Ricks Bar','Be the first to follow Anil Chawla, Tuhin Mehta at Ricks !','','','','http://nh7.in/gigs/anil-chawla-tuhin-mehta-at-ricks/',NULL,NULL,'2012-09-18 14:09:51','2012-09-18 14:09:51',0,'[\"\"]','[\"\"]','','2012-09-22 22:00:00','2012-09-22 00:30:00','anil-chawla-tuhin-mehta-at-ricks-bar',1,NULL),(625,'The Hibernian Jungle','The Hibernian Jungle is a band of Irelands finest young and accomplished musicians, all from varying backgrounds and musical styles, who have been brought together through their communal passion for rock, funk and Irish music.The band will be performing original music, as well as reinterpreting the music of some of the worlds most celebrated rock artists like Led Zeppelin, Talking Heads and Creedence Clearwater Revival. Audiences will also be treated to a feast of Irish rock and blues music inspired by le