,'OKTOBERFEST 2012 at T.L.R. & FRIENDS ','S.S. OKTOBERFEST 2012  SAT 22/09  SUN 06/10\r\nSpiralSeeds Oktoberfest launches simultaneously with the official Munich Oktoberfest in Germany. After the successful 2-week festival at T.L.R. last year, this years Oktoberfest expands under SpiralSeed management to include T.L.R., Elmas, Iron Curtain, Flipside & Grey Garden. \r\n\r\nT.L.R. will feature a full line-up of exceptional live music and club nights with beverage sponsorship by Munich brewery Weihenstephaner, the worlds oldest brewery. Meanwhile, Elmas, Flipside and Grey Garden shall provide mouth-watering food inspired by German and Bavarian culinary traditions. Iron Curtain will curate a programme of films for the duration of the festival including classic selections from German cinema as well as films inspired by beer and comradery, two essential ingredients of Oktoberfest. The grand finale of the Oktoberfest shall of course be the Das Boot Beer Drinking Tournament, where the Oktoberfest King (or Queen) shall be awarded their rightful throne! \r\n\r\n* OKTOBERFEST HIGHLIGHTS *\r\n- T.L.R. offers domestic beers @ Rs.99/- (taxes included!)\r\n- Special Oktoberfest F&B menus at T.L.R., Elmas & Flipside\r\n- Das Boot Beer Drinking Tournament featuring multiple rounds of competitive beer drinking, not for the faint of gut!\r\n- Full schedule of live music and club nights at T.L.R. with special themes including Der Zeitgeist and Der Autobahn.\r\n- Alternative events in Film, Spoken Word & Gastronomy at Iron Curtain, Elmas, Grey Garden and Flipside \r\n\r\n* OKTOBERFEST EVENTS SUMMARY *\r\n\r\nSAT 22/09 9PM T.L.R. ::: DISCO 31 feat. WILD CITY DJ & DJ SU REAL (DER ZEITGEIST)\r\n\r\nSUN 23/09 10AM ELMAS ::: KINDER MUFFIN DECORATION WORKSHOP (Kids Only!)\r\n\r\nSUN 23/09 3PM IRON CURTAIN ::: WERNER HERZOG FILM MARATHON\r\n\r\nWED 26/09 6PM GREY GARDEN ::: OKTOBERFEST SUNSET APERITIVO #1\r\n\r\nTHU 27/09 9PM T.L.R. ::: R.E.D. MAWKIN (LIVE-WIRE ROCK & ROLL) \r\n\r\nFRI 28/09 9PM T.L.R. ::: DRIFT! THE TRIO (LIVID JAZZ) \r\n\r\nSAT 29/09 9PM T.L.R. ::: DISCO 31 feat. TEDDYBOYKILL & HASHBACK HASHISH (DER AUTOBAHN) \r\n\r\nSUN 30/09 3PM IRON CURTAIN ::: GERMAN SILENT FILM MARATHON\r\n\r\nSUN 30/09 6PM FLIPSIDE ::: SWINDLERS LIST feat. Jeet Thayil, Palash Krishna Mehrotra, Colin Fernandes, Tadpole Repertory, & Quizmaster Samir Krishnamurti\r\n\r\nWED 03/10 6PM GREY GARDEN ::: OKTOBERFEST SUNSET APERITIVO #2\r\n\r\nTHU 04/10 9PM T.L.R. ::: BIG BANG BLUES (SOUL EXPLOSION) \r\n\r\nFRI 05/10 9PM T.L.R. ::: BRYAN & THE BANDITS (LATIN LOUNGE) \r\n\r\nSAT 06/10 9PM T.L.R. ::: DAS BOOT BEER DRINKING TOURNAMENT feat. HOST SU REAL + DJ WHITE RABBIT \r\n\r\n+ DAILY SCREENINGS AT 6PM & 9PM AT IRON CURTAIN FOR THE DURATION OF THE FESTIVAL\r\n\r\n* OKTOBERFEST FOOD & DRINK *\r\nCome enjoy hearty Oktoberfest favorites for the belly and the soul. Chefs and creative teams at T.L.R., Elmas, Flipside and Grey Garden will be bringing you the most authentic cuisine inspired by Germany and the Oktoberfest tradition With their respective signature twists to tease & appease all Dilliwallahs!','','http://www.facebook.com/events/106581956162807/','','http://www.facebook.com/events/106581956162807/',NULL,NULL,'2012-09-19 23:45:09','2012-09-19 23:45:09',0,'[\"events@tlrcafe.com\"]','[\"9711117615\\r\",\"\\r\",\"RSVP: 9899383899, 011-46080533\\/44\\r\",\"\"]','','2012-09-22 13:00:00','2012-10-06 23:30:00','oktoberfest-2012-at-tlr-friends',3,NULL),(647,'DJ Ruskin at Blue Frog','DJ Ruskin has established blueFROG as his second home and we\'re delighted to catch his cool, funky, groovy tunes that will make us discover and re-discover his wide range of music that spans genres ranging from afro, latin to cutting edge underground electronica.','http://www.bluefrog.co.in/events/dj-ruskin-2','','','http://www.bluefrog.co.in/events/dj-ruskin-2',NULL,NULL,'2012-09-19 23:49:27','2012-09-19 23:49:28',0,'[\"\"]','[\"\"]','','2012-09-20 23:30:00','2012-09-21 01:30:00','dj-ruskin-at-blue-frog',1,NULL),(648,'KOHRA at Out Of The Box','Kohra is the deep, hypnotic and often grungy mirror image of Madhav Shorey. Raw analog signals and lush soundscapes mixed with percussion sounds and sharp glitches is what can be heard through his mysterious productions. A style that is intelligent enough to mesmerize, yet simple enough to move you.\r\n\r\nConstantly paving the way for a new sub-culture of underground dance music is no task for the timid, which is why he has already become the first Indian to have hit the top 10 charts on global industry standards such as Beatport. As a producer his music has been signed to many well respected international record labels including Sounds Of Earth, Trident Music, Wide Angle Recordings and Echoes Records to name a few.','','','','http://www.thewildcity.com/EN/events.xhtml/event/2280-kohra',NULL,NULL,'2012-09-20 00:00:28','2012-09-20 00:00:28',0,'[\"\"]','[\"\"]','','2012-09-21 21:00:00','2012-09-21 12:00:00','kohra-at-out-of-the-box',1,NULL),(649,'ASH ROY at Area 51','To say that this gentleman alongside his bandmates has had a hand in the progression of India\'s booming electronic music scene would be an understatement. Simply, one of the most successful electronic music acts hailing from India, Jalebee Cartel has consistently challenged the notion that dance music is a Western domain by single handedly putting India on the international \'EDM\' map.\r\n\r\nUsually on electronics as a part of the band, tonight Ash Roy will be offering his services as a DJ, showcasing a healthy dose of the freshest house, techno, miminal and everything in between.','','','','http://www.thewildcity.com/EN/events.xhtml/event/2513-ash-roy',NULL,NULL,'2012-09-20 00:05:45','2012-09-20 00:05:45',0,'[\"\"]','[\"\"]','','2012-09-22 12:05:00','2012-09-22 12:05:00','ash-roy-at-area-51',0,NULL),(650,'Warehouse Jam: DJ Whosane! & Support','\r\n\r\nDJ, producer, composer and engineer, Hussain Babai a.k.a DJ Whosane! has a diverse repertoire. Over the last 20 years he has pioneered the dance music scene in India, broadening the entertainment spectrum and paving the way for a whole industry to develop.\r\n\r\nWith his unique fusion sound and style that has been constantly evolving in an ever-shrinking world of boundaries, his performance can be categorised into 2 primary genres; house and Bollywood. A rocking DJ who\'s partly responsible for the booming electronic music scene in India, he\'s kind of DJ royalty (if that\'s your kind of thing).\r\n\r\nAs for the venue, it may just be the best space in the city.\r\n\r\nSupport from: S.O.N.R, Progressive Brothers, and VJ INKLAB','','','','',NULL,NULL,'2012-09-20 10:47:46','2012-09-20 10:47:46',0,'[\"\"]','[\"\"]','','2012-09-22 20:30:00','2012-09-22 23:30:00','warehouse-jam-dj-whosane-support',1,NULL),(651,'Concert by Tritha Sinha','Tritha\'s spellbinding voice has connected with numerous music lovers from all over the world. Brought up in the culturally intense city of Kolkata, Tritha is one of the most promising talents in the country, equally at home with her Indian Classical music as with Bjork, Janis Joplin, Abida Parveen and Aretha Franklin.\r\n\r\nAs a composer and interpreter she has forged her own unique, inclusive sound and has already gained some critical and popular acclaim for her songs, several of which were used by the Magnum Agency, France for their movies on Women changing India. Tritha is known and loved for her very intense and compelling live performances.\r\n\r\nHer solo performaces involves a workspace around her with her Tibetan bowl, electronic tanpura, a guitar and a mac playing self-composed loops and beats. She sings from her repertoire of Indian classical and originals and also interpretations from her experiences with various musicians from jazz, folk or electronic music or with such musicians as guest artists.','','http://www.facebook.com/events/175463529255882/','','http://www.facebook.com/events/175463529255882/',NULL,NULL,'2012-09-20 11:17:38','2012-09-20 11:17:38',0,'[\"\"]','[\"\"]','','2012-09-25 11:20:00','2012-09-25 11:20:00','concert-by-tritha-sinha',1,NULL),(652,'Ashvin Mani Sharma at Afraa','Ashvin Mani Sharma has been a part of the Indian underground music scene since 1995. He has been producing music and DJ\'ing since 1998 and is one of the co-founders of Jalebee Cartel, now an international techno powerhouse.\r\n\r\nMade up of four members, Arjun Vagale (laptop, mixing, electronics), Ash Roy (vocals and percussions), Ashvin Mani Sharma (laptop and synths) and G-force Arjun (bass guitar), Jalebee has been taking India - and the world - by storm for over five years. From individual DJ sets to live gigs, producing to composing, there seems to be nothing that can get in their way.','','','','http://www.thewildcity.com/EN/events.xhtml/event/1525-ashvin-mani-sharma',NULL,NULL,'2012-09-20 11:23:11','2012-09-20 11:23:11',0,'[\"\"]','[\"\"]','','2012-09-29 11:25:00','2012-09-29 11:25:00','ashvin-mani-sharma-at-afraa',1,NULL),(653,'Ash Roy at Oxygen','To say that this gentleman alongside his bandmates has had a hand in the progression of India\'s booming electronic music scene would be an understatement. Simply, one of the most successful electronic music acts hailing from India, Jalebee Cartel has consistently challenged the notion that dance music is a Western domain by single handedly putting India on the international \'EDM\' map.\r\n\r\nUsually on electronics as a part of the band, tonight Ash Roy will be offering his services as a DJ, showcasing a healthy dose of the freshest house, techno, miminal and everything in between.','','','','http://www.thewildcity.com/EN/events.xhtml/event/2514-ash-roy',NULL,NULL,'2012-09-20 11:29:20','2012-09-20 11:29:20',0,'[\"\"]','[\"\"]','','2012-10-03 11:30:00','2012-10-03 11:30:00','ash-roy-at-oxygen',1,NULL),(654,' FLUX: Sandunes & Ox7gen','FLUX is an attempt is to disrupt and differentiate from the prevailing music scene in India. A departure from the mainstream showcasing the best of world music featuring genres such as indie, nu-disco, chill-wave, synth pop, funk, glitch, and electro hip-hop just to name a few.\r\n\r\nWith monthly nights across Mumbai city, they aim to spread great music across various communities eventually storming our way into Delhi, Pune and Bangalore.\r\n\r\nNo genre egos here - Anything and everything (that sounds good) goes.\r\n\r\nLine up:\r\n\r\nSandunes & Ox7gen','','','','http://www.thewildcity.com/EN/events.xhtml/event/1664-flux-sandunes-ox7gen',NULL,NULL,'2012-09-20 11:43:30','2012-09-20 11:43:30',0,'[\"\"]','[\"\"]','','2012-10-07 11:45:00','2012-10-07 11:45:00','flux-sandunes-ox7gen',0,NULL),(655,'Jodhpur,Rajasthan International Folk Festival','The Royal city of Jodhpur will soon play host to over 250 musicians and performing artists from India and around the world to celebrate Rajasthan\'s rich musical culture. Timed to coincide with Sharad Purnima the brightest full moon of the year in north India, Jodhpur RIFF features a series of spectacular concerts and events based in and around the dazzling backdrop of Mehrangarh Fort. The festival is one of India\'s first annual events to celebrate traditional folk music and arts and is supported by international rock star Sir Mick Jagger from the Rolling Stones, RIFF\'s international patron.\r\n\r\nProgramme Summary\r\n\r\n26 October\r\nOpening Night Variety City Concert\r\n\r\n27 - 29 October\r\nIn Residence - a series of interactive sessions with our custodians of culture\r\nFort Festivities\r\n\r\n27 October\r\nDay breaks with Bhanwari Devi & Patashi Devi\r\nDusk Devotions with the Meghwal of Marwar\r\nLiving Legends - I\r\nMain Stage Performances\r\nClub Mehran Performances\r\n\r\n28 October\r\nDawn fakiri with Kartik Das Baul\r\nDusk Devotions with Gulabnath Jogi\r\nLiving Legends - II\r\nMain Stage Performances\r\nDesert Lounge (all acoustic, traditional  from Rajasthan)\r\n\r\n29 October\r\nScottish dawn with Kaela Rowan\r\nChildrens Folk Morning\r\nMain Stage Performances\r\nClub Mehran RIFF Rustle with Scottish, Sri Lankan, Rajasthani and surprise guest artists\r\n\r\n30 October\r\nClosing Dawn Concert Sahaja Kabir, suno bhai sadho by Prahlad Tipaniya and Party','','','','http://www.thewildcity.com/EN/events.xhtml/event/2458-jodhpur-rajasthan-international-folk-festival-2630-october',NULL,1,'2012-09-20 11:54:06','2012-09-20 11:54:06',0,'[\"\"]','[\"\"]','','2012-10-26 11:50:00','2012-10-30 11:50:00','jodhpurrajasthan-international-folk-festival',3,NULL),(657,'Watch DJ CLEMENT Live in Action!','DJ Clements hope in life is to make people dance and this obviously holds true at each of his performances. Currently rated as top 3 DJs in India for House Music in 2012 by VH1 MYFAVDJ.com, DJ Clement is one of the rare talents to have recently emerged in the EDM category. This self-taught DJ has carved a niche for himself in the competitive music industry. His eclectic style of mixing house,\r\nEDM, hip-hop and even Bollywood music, has generated a huge fan following in his name.','','','','http://gigs.gigatools.com/user/Clement',NULL,NULL,'2012-09-20 15:41:14','2012-09-20 15:41:14',0,'[\"\"]','[\"\"]','','2012-09-21 22:00:00','2012-09-22 00:30:00','watch-dj-clement-live-in-action',1,NULL),(658,'Watch DJ CLEMENT Live in Action!','DJ Clements hope in life is to make people dance and this obviously holds true at each of his performances. Currently rated as top 3 DJs in India for House Music in 2012 by VH1 MYFAVDJ.com, DJ Clement is one of the rare talents to have recently emerged in the EDM category. This self-taught DJ has carved a niche for himself in the competitive music industry. His eclectic style of mixing house,\r\nEDM, hip-hop and even Bollywood music, has generated a huge fan following in his name.','','','','http://gigs.gigatools.com/user/Clement',NULL,NULL,'2012-09-20 15:41:16','2012-09-20 15:41:16',0,'[\"\"]','[\"\"]','','2012-09-22 22:00:00','2012-09-23 00:30:00','watch-dj-clement-live-