 South America), to Cocoon in Frankfurt, Australia, Dubai, Miami, Egypt, Amsterdam, Philippines, Ukraine and across the UK. Thats not to mention his separate appearances at Pete Tongs Wonderland in Ibiza and in countries including Mexico, Russia, USA, Spain, India, Lithuania, Georgia, Austria, Poland, Sweden, Italy and the Channel Islands.\r\n\r\nA global fan base was soon established, and guest mixes on BBC Radio 1, Carl Coxs Global and John Digweeds Transitions radio shows followed, as well as Anil & Dale holding down their own bi-monthly GU Radio show. His DJ profile growing simultaneously and his ever increasing status as a producer, with releases on leading labels like Great Stuff, Cr2, Brique Rouge, and Nic Fanciullis Saved Records, alongside countless awards/reviews from DJMag, iDJ, Mixmag and Beatport. Looking to the future, Anil continues touring across the globe  with everything from deep melodic funk and freaky acid house still all part of his repertoire. His productions continue to gain support from the likes of Richie Hawtin, Laurent Garnier, John Digweed, Pete Tong, Hernan Cattaneo, James Zabiela and Nic Fanciulli  New releases forthcoming on Saved, Bitten, Global Underground, and Tribal Rage will ensure that his name carries on being on the house music cognoscentis lips through into the new decade.','','','','http://gigs.gigatools.com/user/AnilChawla',NULL,NULL,'2012-09-20 16:14:35','2012-09-20 16:14:35',0,'[\"\"]','[\"\"]','','2012-09-21 22:00:00','2012-09-22 00:00:00','anil-chawla-at-pasha',1,NULL),(670,'Spartaque at Leela','','','','','http://gigs.gigatools.com/country/India',NULL,NULL,'2012-09-24 07:55:37','2012-09-24 07:55:37',0,'[\"\"]','[\"\"]','','2012-09-23 22:30:00','2012-09-24 01:30:00','spartaque-at-leela',1,NULL),(671,'EARTHDANCE BANGALORE 2012','<< UNITED BY MUSIC & BERLIN UNDERGROUND >>\r\npresent\r\nEARTHDANCE BANGALORE 2012 at PEBBLE - The Jungle Lounge!\r\n::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::\r\nMark you