y beach establishment Shanti Goa. Shanti Goa has housed some of the biggest music mafias in recent times such as as Cheb-I-Sabbah (USA), Mathew Jonson (Canada), Katrin Vesna (Russia), Jalebee Cartel (India), Tiago Oudman (Portugal), Wolf+Lamb (USA), Talvin Singh (UK), Pawas Gupta (Germany), Tatva Kundalini (India), Bjoern Wilke (Germany), DHR Robijn (Holland), Digital Samsara (Israel), K.Moss (Germany) and Electric Zoo dj-team. Aside from all this, Sashanti has 7 cd compilations to his name and plays at hotpsots in Goa, Mumbai, Bangalore and Delhi. Sunburn Goa 2010 cannot be complete without the Russain Czars musical mlange.','','','','http://gigs.gigatools.com/user/Sashanti',NULL,1,'2012-09-25 19:47:07','2012-10-07 16:50:43',26,'[\"\"]','[\"\"]','','2012-10-12 20:00:00','2012-10-12 23:30:00','sashanti-at-bubble-brunch',1,NULL),(679,'Mad Maxx at The Park Hotel','Max Peterson has been performing and releasing his unique brand of trance music under various project names since 1998. Max was born in San Diego, California in 1979, and spent most of his teenage years in France. In 2000, Max formed the seminal San Francisco trance project \"Biodegadable\" with Samy Guediche of CPU, and Nicolas Oesch of Mekkanikka. In 2001, Max joined up with Davina Elmosnino and formed the trance project Sirius Isness. Max, then started in his solo project in 2007 Max Maxx. The first Mad Maxx album \"Afterworld\", was released beginning of May 2008 on Phantasm Records! The new Mad Maxx album was released in June 2011 on his new label, United Beats Records. Mad Maxx 3rd album is expected to be release in 2013. Be ready for another mystical journey into the inner self.','','','','http://gigs.gigatools.com/user/UBMEMBERS',NULL,1,'2012-09-25 20:12:08','2012-10-07 16:44:43',25,'[\"\"]','[\"\"]','','2012-10-20 08:15:00','2012-10-20 08:15:00','mad-maxx-at-the-park-hotel',1,NULL),(680,'Mad Maxx at Hilltop','Max Peterson has been performing and releasing his unique brand of trance music under vario