ot only provides a platform for professional musicians and bands but also opens its doors to amateur or upcoming artists that want to get more recognition. The genre of music played in the caf is unlimited and varies from jazz/blues to heavy metal/rock or reggae/hip-hop. The caf has also opened a Comic/Anime DVD section where you can get a wide selection of some of the popular comic characters seen and read across the world. With their laid back ambience and warm customer service the caf is a favorite amongst young and old who want to have a quiet moment to themselves or catch up with loved ones over a hot cup of coffee or a steamy bowl of noodles on a cold chilly day or chill out with a tall ice tea or their famous rainbow soda in the hot sweltering days. So dont hold back and let the inner child in you discover the fun that Jumping Bean Caf has in store for you in their menu and events.\r\n\r\nPlease note that the cafe is a \"Self Service Cafe\" and we are CLOSED on TUESDAY\'s.','jumpingbeancafe@gmail.com','http://www.facebook.com/jumpingbeancafedimapur?sk=info',NULL,0,5,NULL,'2012-09-17 11:02:31','2012-09-17 11:02:31',0,'[\"03862 284 619\"]','[\"\"]',NULL),(800,1,'Hotel Grand Sartaj','Add.:- A-3, Green Park, Sri Aurobindo Marg, New Delhi- 16,','','http://www.maharanigroupofhotels.com/grand-sartaj/contact-us.html','',NULL,0,5,NULL,'2012-09-17 11:25:58','2012-09-17 11:25:58',0,'[\"Tel. No.:-\\t+91-11-26561547\\r\",\" \\t+91-11-42657707\\r\",\"Fax No.:-\\t+91-141-2371712\"]','[\"\"]',NULL),(801,3,'E Zone Club','Mahadevpura Outer Ring Road, Near Marathalli Bridge,  Marathahalli , Bangalore','Ezone Club is one amongst the top venues for leisure and entertainment at an affordable price. The venue has excellent card rooms, gym, swimming pool and banquet halls.','','',NULL,0,5,NULL,'2012-09-17 11:38:55','2012-09-17 11:38:55',0,'[\"41719481\"]','[\"\"]',NULL),(802,74,'Club Rhino','312, South Point Mall, Golf Course Road, Gurgaon','Nestled on the top floor of the South Point Mall, Rhino overlooks the swanky neighbourhood of the Golf Course Road in Gurgaon. Rhino is a melting pot for like-minded people. Its a bubbling cauldron of hobnobbing creativity, elbow rubbing minds and jostling eclectic souls. Enjoy live performances over a glass of wine and hors doeuvres or savour its multi cuisine delicacies on its terrace, Rhino merges world music with lip-smacking food.\r\nA concoction of good food, mood and music, Rhino, is a place with myriad experience. The music at Rhino blends in and does not overwhelm the revelers. It rather provides enough space for sharing a thought or a conversation. Anyone and everyone who is deeply connected to music would love to visit Rhino for its vast variety. Its an amalgamation of different individuals finding their own unique world with different music experiences.\r\nInspired by the Rhino, the clubs philosophy, aesthetics and its identity was conceptualized to evoke a feeling of earthy, raw solidity with a timeless appeal.\r\n\r\nTo this end, extensive use of natural materials was made, with minimal treatment to allow the innate character of the material speak for itself. A palette of wood, iron, copper and granite was juxtaposed with elegant touches of lighter materials like rope, fabric and screens to create interest. The ambience thus provides the right balance of stimuli and comfort.\r\n\r\nRhino is designed as an exciting journey through a volumetric play of spaces  the journey begins from the moment you step under the mammoth light feature which overlooks the dynamic double height area with a stage for live performances. This leads to an intimate single height area with the bar-overlooking the lush outdoors, and finally a relaxing outdoor dining area with one of the best views over the city. A single destination to cater to myriad moods.','','http://www.facebook.com/clubrhinoindia',NULL,0,5,NULL,'2012-09-17 13:36:11','2012-09-17 13:36:11',0,'[\"+91 9560700123, 9717778683\"]','[\"\"]',NULL),(803,74,'Media Cafe','The location: South Point Mall, next to Genpact, Golf Course Road, DLF Phase V, Gurgaon.','Indias first pub by media people, of media people, for media people.  TMC  The Media Caf  has been founded by well-known former Lintas hands Sudha Natrajan and Raghav Subramanian. Location: in the heart of Gurgaon, within touching distance of the Gurgaon Golf Club.\r\nBoth media veterans with 20 plus years of experience behind them, recently left Lintas Media Group and the agency world to start up on their own. The duo has launched two businesses from their base in Gurgaon/NCR. The first business is The Media Consultancy, a strategic consultancy specialising in new-age consumer research, brand and ROI analytics and modelling, media content and training. The second one is The Media Caf, which is a first of its kind media, advertising and marketing hangout.\r\nThe Media Caf is a place the media/advertising fraternity can call its own. Where one can bond, learn, gossip, have lots of fun and discussions. Afternoon, evening and late night, it promises to be the place for non-stop entertainment, great soul food, and intelligent liquor! And easy on the wallet!','','',NULL,0,5,NULL,'2012-09-19 23:22:09','2012-09-19 23:22:09',0,'[\"0124-4222159 \"]','[\"\"]',NULL),(804,4,'Area 51','Baner Hills, Javahar, Taluka Haveli, Baner Road, Pune','Area 51, is India\'s first 4-level entertainment lounge. It serves as a multi-purpose venue and has a throbbing discotheque at heart. The unique dome architecture, lavish interiors and state-of-the-art light and sound hardware need to be experienced to be believed','http://www.area51india.com/home.html','',NULL,0,5,NULL,'2012-09-20 00:04:19','2012-09-20 00:04:19',0,'[\"Area 51, Pune phone number 020 66035000, +91 9922442000 \"]','[\"\"]',NULL),(805,1,'Olive Bar And Kitchen','One Style Mile,Kalka Das Marg , New Mehrauli ,  Delhi','For details , contact,\r\n\r\n\r\nOne Style Mile,Kalka Das Marg , New Mehrauli ,  Delhi\r\n9810235472, 29574444,